{
  "stem": "24259.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were hiding in a stack of hay, essentially, in a barn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was just the barn was full of hay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would store it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, the barns in those days and in that area were not the same as we know it now.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were just like-- the roofs were made out of hay themselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and some of them were very simple structures.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We would stay there the whole time, of course, for fear of being discovered.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If we were discovered, obviously, we would all be killed, as well as the people that were hiding us were also in danger of being killed, as was happened many times to others.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Food was almost non-existent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even the farmers themselves had, you know, very meager food availability.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We would actually sometimes share food that they would throw out to the pigs and so forth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father would, you know, go out, and kind of scavenge through and find things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would eat-- occasionally, he'd go out and find berries and things in the woods, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And somehow we were able to maintain staying alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From this first farmer who kept us for two or three months, my father found another farmer that was willing to take us in.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at this time, he dug a hole in a barn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The farmer and my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They dug a hole in the farm inside where they kept the cows in a barn.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they covered up with planks, and of course, with straw over it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they made an entrance through the manger trough where they fed the cows.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was the entrance to go in inside the hole.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
